Fotizona Guard: Hey, stop that carriage! We need to inspect
your luggage.

Thief Nora: Oh, it's the guards! If they've come this far,
we can relax!

General Store Libra: Is there such a foolish thing! They are
imposters, prepare to fight!

General Store Libra: I don't care who you are, but you've
had bad luck! We have adventurers from the Adventurer's
Guild here!

Fotizona Fake Guard: Adventurer's Guild...! If that's the
case, we definitely can't let them escape!

Fotizona Fake Guard: The grudge of the Tomos plundering gang
that was annihilated... I will settle it here!
Clea: Libra-san, please step back. Leave this to us!

General Store Libra: It was a great decision to take this
job! If we hand these guys over to the Empire, we'll make a
fortune.

Clea: From here on is Fotizona, right? Can we consider the
request complete?

General Store Libra: Of course, it's a little inconvenient,
but could you come to the inn to receive your reward?

General Store Libra: I want to hand over the reward for
delivering these guys, so I plan to book an inn on Fotizona
Main Street. Please rely on me.

General Store Libra: Remember what we talked about earlier,
okay?
Thief Nora: Did you talk about something?
Clea: No... It's just small talk.
